title: "Apple halting US sales of Series 9
text: Ultra 2 smartwatches over blood-oxygen patent dispute"
source_name: "The move comes after an order in October from the US International Trade Commission that could bar Apple from importing its Apple Watches after finding the devices violate medical technology company Masimo's patent rights."
